cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use or build on the xOP standard, please cite it as below."
title: "xOP — The open standard for reusable AI operating rules"
abstract: >-
  xOP is a portable, model-agnostic standard for reusable AI operating rules. An xOP captures a
  single recurring judgment: the condition that makes a rule apply, what should flip it, and the
  line it must never cross. Its moral center is a single asymmetric gate: fp_on_warranted == 0.
  All published xOPs are DESIGNED — well-formed, not yet independently validated.
type: software
authors:
